filament_end_gcode:
; Filament-specific end gcode 
;END gcode for filament
filament_start_gcode:
; Filament gcode
;M412 D25
;M412 S1  ; Enable Runout
;M900 K0.12 ; Linear advance spring constant - based on sunlu blue petg

{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_E3DD.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0975{endif}  ; set E3DD advance
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_MODEL_CYBER.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0975{endif}  ; set cybermk2 advance

{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0975 {endif}  ;  Guess 
;;;;;;{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_SWITCH_E3D.*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.4} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.38{endif}  ;GUESS Switchwire Bowden
{if printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_OS_KLIPPER.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*HOTEND_AFTERBURNER_E3D.*/ and printer_notes=~/.*PRINTER_NOZZLE_CHT*/ and nozzle_diameter[0]==0.6} SET_PRESSURE_ADVANCE ADVANCE=0.0525{endif}  ; 2022-03-03
name: Ankun PETG @CHT
